Package com.example.qr_check_in.ModelClasses

Class Event

java.lang.Object
com.example.qr_check_in.ModelClasses.Event
public class Event extends Object
The Event class represents an event within the system. It contains information such as title, date, time, location, description, organizer, attendees, and the number of attendees.
